Badge fix verification:
- .svg was appearing in rendered badge labels (e.g., "tests.svg" instead of "tests")
- Root cause: .svg appended after query string params instead of in URL path
- Pattern: shields.io expects .svg as the file extension in the path segment,
  before the ? query string. Query params like &label= are rendered as-is.
- All 5 badges affected: tests, license, issues, python, emacs
